        {title: 'Turn your customers into loyal influencers', 
        text: 'Budss helps businesses harness the exponential power of loyal customers for acquisition and retention.',
        src: '../../images/benefit__item-1__desktop.png',
        },
        {title: 'Harness the power of buying in bulk',
